---

<footer style="border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
  <div class="page-container" style="padding-top: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 4rem); padding-bottom: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 4rem);">
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); margin-bottom: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 4rem);">
      <div>
        <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">elly</h3>
        <p class="body-small" style="max-width: 280px;">
          Self-hosted AI notebook. Notes, diary, calendar, habits, tasks, AI assistant. Your data, yours.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4 style="font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-ink-tertiary); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Product</h4>
        <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem;">
          <li><a href="https://patreon.com/kxnotes" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-ink-secondary); text-decoration: none;">Patreon</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://github.com/Kxetch/kx-notes" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-ink-secondary); text-decoration: none;">GitHub</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://discord.gg/kxnotes" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-ink-secondary); text-decoration: none;">Discord</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4 style="font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-ink-tertiary); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Resources</h4>
        <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem;">
          <li><a href="https://github.com/Kxetch/kx-notes/blob/main/SECURITY.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-ink-secondary); text-decoration: none;">Security</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://github.com/Kxetch/kx-notes/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-ink-secondary); text-decoration: none;">Contributing</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://github.com/Kxetch/kx-notes/blob/main/LICENSE" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-ink-secondary); text-decoration: none;">License</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4 style="font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-ink-tertiary); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Legal</h4>
        <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem;">
          <li><a href="https://github.com/Kxetch/kx-notes/blob/main/CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-ink-secondary); text-decoration: none;">Code of Conduct</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="padding-top: 1.5rem; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;">
      <p class="body-small">
        AGPL-3.0. No tracking. Your hardware, your data.
      </p>
      <p class="body-small">
        Built with care.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
